587
00:40:44,520 --> 00:40:45,080
Mm.

588
00:40:46,080 --> 00:40:46,800
I...

589
00:40:47,500 --> 00:40:49,000
Haré lo que tú digas.

590
00:41:10,600 --> 00:41:11,560
Dulces sueños, Duang.

591
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:17,520
Dulces sueños.

592
